Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:40.27,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}将爱埋没于伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.71,0:00:44.94,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}由腐败中诞生的世界所拥有的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.96,0:00:47.64,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}是繁华的绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.26,0:00:51.65,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}放生抑或杀生都是我们的罪业
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.66,0:00:54.72,OP_cht2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}如猪狗一般发笑 流泪
